# Process Brief — {{PROCESS_NAME}}

> **Status**: {{STATUS}} | **Version**: {{PROCESS_VERSION}} | **Owner**: {{PROCESS_OWNER_PRIMARY}}
> **Last Updated**: {{LAST_UPDATED}}

---

## L1.1 — Triggers

```yaml
trigger:
  type: {{TRIGGER_TYPE}}
  source: {{TRIGGER_SOURCE}}
  initial_state: {{TRIGGER_INITIAL_STATE}}
  preconditions:
{% for pc in PRECONDITIONS %}
    - "{{pc}}"
{% endfor %}
  post_conditions:
{% for pc in POST_CONDITIONS %}
    - "{{pc}}"
{% endfor %}
```

---

## L1.2 — Inputs

| Input | Source | Required | Used In Step |
|---|---|---|---|
{% for input in INPUTS %}
| {{input.name}} | {{input.source}} | {{input.required}} | {{input.used_in_step}} |
{% endfor %}

---

## L1.3 — Roles & Responsibilities

> **TTL Note**: Role names, contacts, and team assignments are volatile. Add `@valid_until=YYYY-Q#` for each role during generation.

{% for role in ROLES %}
### {{role.name}} (`{{role.id}}`)<!-- TTL: @valid_until={{ROLE_TTL}} -->

- **Persona**: {{role.persona}}
- **Nature**: {{role.nature}}
- **Home Team**: {{role.home_team}}<!-- TTL: @valid_until={{ROLE_TTL}} -->
- **Collaboration Context**: {{role.collaboration_context}}
- **Boundaries**: {{role.boundaries}}
{% if role.nature == "conditional" %}
- **Binding Rule**:
{% for rule in role.binding_rule %}
  - {{rule.condition}} → {{rule.binds_to}}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

---

## L1.4 — Step Sequence

{% for step in STEPS %}
### {{step.id}} — {{step.name}}

- **Executor**: {{step.executor_role}}
- **Inputs**: {{step.inputs | join(", ") or "None"}}
- **Actions**:
{% for action in step.actions %}
  1. {{action}}
{% endfor %}
- **Outputs**: {{step.outputs | join(", ") or "None"}}
- **Duration**: {{step.duration.type}} — {{step.duration.value}}
{% if step.trace_status %}
- **Trace Status**: {{step.trace_status}}<!-- Phase 3 Trace Mode -->
{% if step.trace_last_check %}- **Last Checked**: {{step.trace_last_check}}{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% if step.loop_back_target %}
- **Loop Back To**: {{step.loop_back_target}}
{% endif %}
{% if step.related_invariant %}
- **Related Invariants**: {{step.related_invariant | join(", ")}}
{% endif %}
- **Next**:
{% for next in step.next %}
  - {% if next.condition %}**IF** {{next.condition}} **THEN** → {{next.goto}}{% else %}(default) → {{next.goto}}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% endfor %}

---

## L1.5 — Decision Points

{% for decision in DECISIONS %}
### {{decision.id}} — {{decision.description}}

- **Type**: {{decision.type}}
- **Condition Quality**: {{decision.condition_quality}}
- **Affects**: {{decision.affects}}
{% if decision.type == "binary" %}
- **Condition**: {{decision.condition}}
- **If YES** → {{decision.yes_goto}}
- **If NO** → {{decision.no_goto}}
{% elif decision.type == "nested" %}
```yaml
nested_logic:
{{decision.nested_logic | indent(2)}}
```
{% elif decision.type == "decision_table" %}
| {{decision.table_headers | join(" | ")}} |
|---|{% for h in decision.table_headers %}---|{% endfor %}
{% for row in decision.table_rows %}
| {{row | join(" | ")}} |
{% endfor %}
{% elif decision.type == "timing" %}
- **Timing Rule**: {{decision.timing_rule}}
{% elif decision.type == "attribute" %}
- **Affected Attribute**: {{decision.attribute_name}}
- **Determination Rule**: {{decision.attribute_rule}}
{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

