- **Extraction Status**: {{STATE_EXTRACTION_STATUS}}

| State ID | State Name | Terminal | Failure Type |
|---|---|---|---|
{% for state in STATES %}
| {{state.id}} | {{state.name}} | {{state.terminal}} | {{state.failure_type}} |
{% endfor %}

**Transitions**:

| From | To | Triggered By |
|---|---|---|
{% for t in TRANSITIONS %}
| {{t.from}} | {{t.to}} | {{t.triggered_by}} |
{% endfor %}

