## L1.7 — RACIO Matrix

| Step |{% for role in ROLES %} {{role.id}} |{% endfor %}
|---|---|{% for role in ROLES %}---|{% endfor %}
{% for row in RACIO_MATRIX %}
| {{row.step_id}} |{% for cell in row.assignments %} {{cell}} |{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}

**Legend**: R = Responsible, A = Accountable, C = Consulted, I = Informed, O = Oversight

